28:40.000 --> 28:41.260
Bom pun perlukan duit.

28:42.200 --> 28:43.160
Betul tu.

28:43.440 --> 28:44.840
Kalau begitu, lebih baik berhenti kerja awal

28:44.840 --> 28:46.040
dan balik ke kampung.

28:46.400 --> 28:47.480
Betul tu.

28:49.400 --> 28:50.280
Ah Yi.

28:51.560 --> 28:52.320
Mari tolong.

28:52.480 --> 28:53.640
Baiklah.

29:02.720 --> 29:03.640
Ah Yi.

29:04.240 --> 29:05.040
Awak tahu tak,

29:05.400 --> 29:06.600
